HEADWORD: Churning
<hw>Churn"ing</hw>, <pos>n.</pos> <sn>1.</sn> <def>The act of one who
churns.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><sn>2.</sn> <def>The quantity of butter made at one
